ll back up.\n\nSince ticketing systems are task oriented, they donâ€™t generally have the capabilities necessary for longer term â€œcase tracking and work order managementâ€. As disaster relief progresses, it is often necessary to migrate information from a ticketing system to other systems, such as a CRM system for â€œindividual case trackingâ€ and the Work Order System for â€œcollaborative work order managementâ€.','recFN89wM7ldOSmK8','recUiHoYSXjwhqwsl, recBphHepquvwUyIH','','','','help-desk'),(431,'recQYxttX2I6qsypu','Help Desk Software Recommendations','Recommendations','Using \"help desk\" software (also known as online ticketing software) can help you ensure that every inquiry that\'s come into your organization or group has been addressed.','recFN89wM7ldOSmK8','recBphHepquvwUyIH','','','Devin',''),(432,'recLy08xrAyPk6uZm','High Resolution Maps','data','Gain more situational awareness through images taken by satellite or drone.','recqVYJyuOteg4eEF','','','','',''),(433,'recw0ntkjAVLcDyq3','home','glossary','','','recqPkDhp14BArq8P','','','',''),(434,'recXAVByqbQQPHx4q','Hospital Data','data','Ground choices about resource allocation, referrals, and projects based on baseline understandings of hospitals.','rec0Z49MeFdR1j2IM','','','','',''),(435,'recsFMop0bv8gaAum','hosted','glossary','','','recpqz9DeaK4ryVk4','','','',''),(436,'recHjAGJjAQxL0naU','Hours','data','Anticipate project timeliness, individual efficacy, and budget needs through hour tracking.','recpMPHSM9vY43lnn','','','','',''),(437,'rec2w1EOpVXXljGtY','housing','glossary','','','rec8nK0qKXdkp1jbR','','','',''),(438,'recSwdH66DOR8TJF0','How to set up the chat','Tags','','','','','','',''),(439,'recu9BqjQViflaxC9','Hub Network','Toolboxes','','rec14GvxnUyQQ183Y','','','','',''),(440,'reczfrZqOk9mtvinF','Human Resources','Tool Type','','','recYLESKN2qudS1I8','','','','human-resources'),(441,'rectnkS4K463mQGCR','Human Resources','Tags','','recIMA1ty9QITjcq5, rec5s6dhq2DaMOwud, recHjAGJjAQxL0naU, recrONMGyKFnwTOhf, recfzSIcI0HCmL5uq, recAthyUz5MFleB3K, recPOhN4DXWRMmYOy','recbWK3L093KDci3w, recJfBIWH4MnZ7COJ, recLSr4OMUDfLFHfi, recVNT6Ey09i0EzVe','recx8JohA3SXDWFrP, recQ8Hfi7reUyLfvZ, recZ3YsoZ4GHiE4gh','','',''),(442,'recpMPHSM9vY43lnn','Human Resources','glossary','','','recYLESKN2qudS1I8, recDVYNCne1Cd5L4R','','','',''),(443,'rec9tKLenSPug18ER','human rights','','','','recyBFjmWoZihzc39','','','',''),(444,'recd8ln08AyBVuQpT','human services','Skills','','','','','','',''),(445,'recdcveRb1arT5kZU','Human Services Directory','Toolboxes','After a disaster, relief providers need good information about where to refer victims for \"human services\" assistance such as homeless shelters, mental health counselling and food pantries. Unlike local business information, which has been made readily available via the internet over a decade ago, â€œhuman serviceâ€ information is not.  Directories of human service providers are usually managed by state government contractors who use proprietary database systems that not even most VOADs â€” let alone disaster survivors â€” can access.\n\nTo access this information, people have to call directory assistance like they did in the 1990s to talk with their local 211 call center operator.  This leads to confusion and wasted time for survivors, and creates a problem for relief providers who want to track that their clients are receiving up to date information and following up on referrals.\n','rec3Kg9cOs40Sh6MK, recCLZfQaeOhzXK7a, rec31B4uFy6AxksQH, recdZk6CZiTywlVag, reczaaEDsAz9p6eYf, recfC03GSAMAdwx0B, rect0A3jN5DvRLiHH, recEtIwLKglEs5fjQ, reckRvwsJ4rLE7Ul8','','','','',''),(446,'recC4G6vxnnUoPfGi','human trafficking','glossary','','','recp9ubVucPp0MVmL, rec2MwT1DEUSVkK0Q, reciCqGyov1XYX4vW','','','',''),(447,'recWN5ptSOY0SlbEc','human-machine-hybrid','glossary','','','recdEInugFYktw0WM','','','',''),(448,'recg9A9tMyxCkKOJR','humanitairian','glossary','','','reclmAm6bGKBDD6wm','','','',''),(449,'recCnKXzx3sKmTxKJ','humanitarian