which action is based','rec0YJGoEQ3yZTUSo, reckaDnQkHKr7Tdbb, rec3x2wFL96ycvBsa, recXAVByqbQQPHx4q, recme7gn4qSchYhDm, recrp7Z1anRl89i0s','','','','',''),(479,'rec9urNMuVRTtAbop','Innovation','Tags','','','recFP3FTuTP0J2Pj8, recxrnpgp5cv0W8nK, recFppmoktl8wBcey, recslUQnEDpEeDNSr, recusMtU7IilmWGQT, recHeRzlyvI6CJlm5, rec4lMMrTt8Lx0y2L, rec3p2gT3v6xR48GI, recip7WzvfZiDiGaK, rec44lFYdj5uZXjxO','rec5IF6N3UtUOpNvE','','',''),(480,'rec7LM3X3UJHTWur3','Innovation Company','Tags','','','','','','',''),(481,'recJuIbtJPjUfr63p','Innovation Company','glossary','','','recHqZVr1BFqb3w1D','','','',''),(482,'recx4HMrpCROtGtnH','Innovation Labs','Tags','','rec5zBZGmpjhL9lpD, reccLHAWzHbWmq50l','recFppmoktl8wBcey','','','',''),(483,'recOKKNHXL5NwzhJL','Innovation Labs','glossary','','','recWo0NqK2VuO5Glu, rec1NZFKhWoJr736y, rec1CbzNYt6oHlGC7','','','',''),(484,'recjBVDcyTKNYxM9u','Insurance Analysis','Tasks','What does insurance cover? Do the paperwork for that as well.','recReqN39G0tE5lvn','','','','',''),(485,'recexrlKURqRkwXei','Intake Inventory Manager','Use Case','Ensure requests and donations are respected by keeping inventory information and request queues up to date.','rec67LQ7smpAw91Gt, recNweu1ptwANSAdh','','','','',''),(486,'recmeOAEqc9mtVNTq','Integrating CiviCRM with your Website','Tutorials','One of CiviCRM\'s main advantages is that it exists as a component of popular FLO content management systems WordPress, Drupal and Joomla.  As such, it\'s easy to use CiviCRM to power a wide range of functionality on your website.\n\nWeb forms can collect information about supporters, volunteers and survivors via your groupâ€™s website. Individuals can be organized into segmented communications lists depending on the information they enter into the form.\n\nEmail newsletters can be sent to people depending on information associated with their profiles. For example, if people completing the â€œVolunteer Formâ€ are asked on which day(s) of the week and in which neighborhood(s) theyâ€™re interested in volunteering, that criteria can be used to create segmented lists of people whoâ€™re interested in specific times and places.\n\nOnline payments is a standard feature in many CRMs. This allows groups to process donations on their own website, which allows them to control the donation experience and retain donor information.\n\nProfiles exist for every person in a CRM. Profiles can be configured for different types of use cases. Volunteers, for example, might have information about their work preferences; while survivors might have information about their specific situation. These profiles are often also designed to log interactions. For example, if someone volunteers successfully, that interaction can be recorded; or, if someone is canvassed, that fact (and the results of the canvass) can be indicated.\n\nOnline Calendar and events management can be used for a variety of functions, including ticket sale processing for fundraising â€œgalaâ€ style events or RSVPing for volunteer events.','rec3NEj4ZcZ6KT0hA, recdZk6CZiTywlVag','recZHSZypSFHafKIW','','','',''),(487,'recCvDZf8lhusZXzp','interactive graphic','glossary','','','recH0kwnZWjJUT02E','','','',''),(488,'recyPXrEx67n426FE','interactive map','glossary','','','rec2MwT1DEUSVkK0Q','','','',''),(489,'rec478jcu2UFRzEUL','Internal Coordination','Challenges','Coordinating within any group, whether it\'s an emergent, adhoc grassroots group or an established nonporift, is essential for delivering appropriate and timely relief to those who need it.  Emergency situations make everything more urgent, so having written protocols for making decisions and moving resources (especially money) becomes particularly important.\n\nWithin your relief operation, however, you\'ll need to determine what criteria people and projects need to meet in order to access scarce resources.','recnebUtIIFB2MmCh, recNKcrxQjV2NUa49, recerWLHj3n60GIuS','','','','',''),(490,'recdvuRRZxgFjZBmf','Interviewee for Humanitarian Programming','Use Case','Benefit from incoming resources by advocating for your community\'s needs and capacities through participation in development agency interviews and workshops.','reczlQNhpfNosVLvS, rec8teGY7CnU71x1J','','','','',''),(491,'recmNVNohHFgwzAkF','Interviewer for Humanitarian Programming','Use Case','Shape a program\'s design or implementation to be more locally relevant by listening to local community representatives in interviews and workshops.','reczlQNhpfNosVLvS, recW4gfJIWhRniBIg','recEOFP1tUQ1gAN25, recBRw30Cs2zjBsle','','','',''),(492,'recoIyMTVQ2eAn7cx','intranet and record-keeping tool','glossary','','','rectDW4pQ5lV32N1t','','','',''),(493,'recYNoE635ItxK5Uv','inventory','Skills','','','','','','',''),(494,'recGNmry0f1CbdPZx','inventory','Skills','','','','','','',''),(495,'recEDz3Oivbz6yVZI','Inventory Handler','Use Case','Increase the effectiveness of dispatch by maintaining the organization condition of physical resources in warehouses and other sites.','recAK1ItvntOMXoLe','recmQwgEi1LbNQaDy','','','',''),(496,'recEzW5HwohYyLj9N','Inventory Management','Toolboxes','Before, during and after a disaster, many relief groups have to perform a wide range of logistical tasks, create a specific set of needs that FLO software solutions can meet:\n\nrequesting and receiving inventory items\ntracking inventory at multiple facilities\nsending inventory to people in need\ngenerating reports about activities\nsharing up-to-date inventory information with stakeholders such as government agencies such as FEMA, nonprofit and community groups, donors and the general public\ndeveloping an awareness of the other relief providers in the area\nWithout a software tool set to help organizations meet these needs, groups are often left using spreadsheets and personal relationships to make sense of the disaster logistics environment. Many people suffer and many resources are wasted because a coordinated disaster logistics network doesn\'t exist â€” and it very well could.','rec3Kg9cOs40Sh6MK, recCLZfQaeOhzXK7a, recNy7Vep3mOEjEAY, rec6AGCHolWP5vDvs, recZjjj5j5FcsxfAU','rec9qW0uW0ugxtjtT','','','',''),(497,'rec6AGCHolWP5vDvs','Inventory Management with ERPs','Tutorials','It\'s useful to think of the core information you need to know to do any type of inventory management:\n\nWho is giving you inventory? It\'s likely that some inventory will appear from individuals, but most will come from organizationsâ€”businesses, government agencies, and other relief groups. Create a list of inventory \"supplies\".\nWhere are you storing it? Are you storing inventory in one or more locations? Create a list of your \"facilities\", including name, address, contact people, features and any organizational schema worth noting, such as a bun system.\nWhere will it be going? Are you giving inventory to individuals directly, through case management and or via a distribution hub or relief site in the affected community? Create a list of these \"sites\".','recEzW5HwohYyLj9N, rec3Kg9cOs40Sh6MK','recPxlJDZ9xvTIQzX, rec9qW0uW0ugxtjtT','','','',''),(498,'recncEtWZQvwkXKle','Investing in CiviCRM for Disaster Use Cases','Recommendations','CiviCRM could become a fantastic disaster contact and case management solution that any VOAD could use for itself and in partnership with others. And since the solution would be FLO, any organization wanting to become active in disaster relief would be able to â€œspin upâ€ their own system and keep ownership over their own data. At the very least, the existence of a CiviCRM powered alternative to CAN will encourage VisionLink to be more responsive to the community of VOADs who use CAN. Of course, CiviCRM can play well with CAN by being configured to export and share data using CAN-compliant format and standards. Compliance with Federal requirements and standards is something that could also be built into a CiviCRM component, as could a basic reporting mechanism that would enable each disaster case management deployments to share basic identity information about clients to ensure that people aren\'t enrolled in more than one case management system to get â€œdouble benefitsâ€.\n\nNational VOAD and larger VOAD groups should come together to ensure CiviCRM works well for disaster relief. I recommend pursuing the following course of activity:\n\nDevelop a case management template (in XML) that could be imported into any CiviCRM to turn it into a disaster case management system. Estimated cost: under $10,000.\n\nFund the development of a user interface for CiviCase configuration. There is a fundraising campaign currently underway to raise $30,000 to create a user interface that would make it much easier for people to customize CiviCase.\n\nDevelop capacity within the NVOAD network for managing CiviCRM hosting, either by hiring a CiviCRM expert or contracting with a provider like CiviHosting.com.\n\nRun database management trainings so VOADs learn how databases can be used to solve a wide range of challenges they encounter.','','recZHSZypSFHafKIW','','','',''),(499,'recgxkGC7MBmrQGg6','java','glossary','','','rec9QLNLnj9F1V5y8, recZihoX7mf8buPBY','','','',''),(500,'recPOhN4DXWRMmYOy','Job Profiles','data','Define what characteristics need to be represented and tasks fulfilled on a project by creating job profiles.','recpMPHSM9vY43lnn','','','','',''),(501,'recn0MqigMENe8pKW','Journalists','Use Case','','recy9bOMa0tDoHhsN','recVVEZ7uCrldv0jH, rectf6DkZKVkmm3c0','','','',''),(502,'recstKa27j0EY5Tzg','Kathmandu Living Labs','Toolboxes','','rec7QKAjIf7Jj9KF3','','','','',''),(503,'recutVU6cRqBvkqeM','Keep responders in communication with each other and with the wider world by doing the shipping and logistics around hardware for Information Communication Technology (ICT).','Workflows','','reckNyxDnvAtVO82p, recd6fTha4M5e2oEg','','','','Willow',''),(504,'recQb1iriEZd7d8vB','Keep spreadsheets and databases up to date and clean','Workflows','','reckNyxDnvAtVO82p, recZoqL43IBjFlcAZ','','','','Willow',