 a user interface for CiviCase configuration. There is a fundraising campaign currently underway to raise $30,000 to create a user interface that would make it much easier for people to customize CiviCase.\n\nDevelop capacity within the NVOAD network for managing CiviCRM hosting, either by hiring a CiviCRM expert or contracting with a provider like CiviHosting.com.\n\nRun database management trainings so VOADs learn how databases can be used to solve a wide range of challenges they encounter.','recNKcrxQjV2NUa49, rechRM6Mk5F2Mw0FV','recZHSZypSFHafKIW','','','Devin',''),(945,'rec15Oy0yXmnuAmQU','Using CiviCRM to make a Directory','Tutorials','','recwCY7kOuRqdQTuB, recdZk6CZiTywlVag','recZHSZypSFHafKIW','','','',''),(946,'recl1CISnR7pL4ORR','Using Data for Advocacy','Tasks','Advocates and activists use data to push for change.','recWNX91VUaintM4q, recP5VA7d5HIfa1O9','','','','',''),(947,'reczG1cvGoSTyrCSK','Using Data for Funding Allocation','Tasks','Funders access dataset to inform further distribution (or removal) of funds','recgtHhKhQbNQ0Uzw, recP5VA7d5HIfa1O9','','','','',''),(948,'rec8Ni8drv8Y7ZnCo','Using Data for Resource Allocation','Tasks','Leaders use dataset to inform their strategy and to work with funders and agencies for better resource allocation ','recJRHDHvmFYmTF35, recP5VA7d5HIfa1O9','','','','',''),(949,'rec0BbSfh3O9rsmyu','Using Existing Aerial Imagery','Tasks','Locate and liberate aerial imagery from as recently before the shock as possible','recDfY2UZj521EIWn, recReqN39G0tE5lvn','','','','',''),(950,'recCIw9j0UVrrTFGf','Using Existing Datasets','Tasks','Locate and liberate preexisting environmental and demographic data about an area','recq6zCRgVjaHfNaQ, recReqN39G0tE5lvn','','','','',''),(951,'recUYQ5rwd7AaDnUL','Using Gmail to Manage another Email Account','Tutorials','','recFmTEL3UuvxzYJz','recZrRu7MTj3Sv9d2','','','',''),(952,'recuonNXVQCAV91A8','Using LIDAR','Tasks','Use lydar to determine where collapsed buildings are','recDfY2UZj521EIWn, re